public class ConstAnalyzer extends standalone.com.sun.source.util.TreeScanner<Void,​standalone.com.sun.source.util.Trees>
This AST scanner analyzes local variables to determine if they are locally assigned and can be assumed constant or not.

    • ConstAnalyzer

      public ConstAnalyzer​(ElementKind variableKind, boolean initializationOnly)
      Create a constant variable analyzer on the given kind of variable.
      Parameters:
      variableKind - the variable kind to analyze (if null, analyzes all kinds of variables)
      initializationOnly - only takes into account direct assignments and not self-dependent modifications
